response.original_title: 1989 Lowry in the North East Animation and Music Workshop
response.overview: Helen Sinclair Head of Education Dept. invited Sheila and Hugh Nankivell to run a combined animation/music workshop to help folks explore the work of Lowry in the North East further. All ages took part - to GREAT effect!
response.title: 1989 Lowry in the North East Animation and Music Workshop
